  <Collapse title='The Story Behind Santisify'>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>
          The name <strong>Santisify</strong> is a purposeful fusion of two foundational concepts:
          <strong>Sanctity</strong> and <strong>Simplify</strong>. It is more than just a brand; it
          is a declaration of our mission and a reflection of the value we strive to deliver to
          every user.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <strong>Sanctity</strong> represents our core ambition. In an increasingly complex and often
          chaotic digital landscape, we champion what is pure, reliable, and trustworthy. We believe
          your data, your attention, and your digital experience should be treated with integrity and
          respect. "Sanctity" embodies our commitment to creating a pristine and secure environment—a
          sanctuary where quality is paramount and your trust is sacred.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <strong>Simplify</strong> represents our method for achieving that ambition. Technology should
          empower, not overwhelm. It should remove barriers, not create them. We are dedicated to the
          relentless pursuit of elegance through simplicity. We distill complex processes into intuitive
          actions, eliminate unnecessary clutter, and design with profound clarity. We transform the
          daunting into the effortless.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          Thus, <strong>Santisify</strong> was born: <strong
            >to simplify technology to its purest, most powerful form.</strong
          > It is the act of purifying the user experience. Our name is a promise—a pledge to cleanse
          digital interaction of its frustrations and to sanctify it with seamless, intelligent, and
          empowering simplicity.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Welcome to a state of purified performance. Welcome to Santisify.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </Collapse>
  <Collapse title='About your avatar?'>
