          lines are concise and smooth, and the outline is round and soft, giving people a cute and
          lovely feeling. There are no sharp edges and corners, which can quickly arouse people's
          affection and conform to the public's aesthetic preference for cute - style images.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          Color Application: It uses a light blue background, which is fresh and elegant. The main
          image is mainly light pink and white, with details such as pink blush. The color
          saturation is low, and the overall color tone is soft, creating a warm and healing
          atmosphere, which is very comfortable visually.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
