          effect, adding a touch of "holiness" to the originally cute image. It echoes the text
          "santisify" below (which has the meaning tendency of sanctifying and purifying), giving
          the cute image an additional layer of unique meaning and interest, and making the design
          more layered and connotative.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          Style Orientation: The whole design belongs to the healing and cute style. From the shape
          to the color and then to the element combination, it all revolves around creating a
          relaxed, pleasant and warm visual experience. It can well attract the audience who like
          the cute and warm style, and is convenient to convey a friendly and cute personal image
          and emotion in social scenarios.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </Collapse>

